  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-b296b8b3-add5-4678-9dd7-4337355c9178\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c570c8c7-4940-46a7-92e9-3e3164769dce\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1d1fe22a-e1bf-49c1-8ed3-8d5559ed8b08\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1f417c7f-e3d1-4887-b6a4-bf0e12d91fce\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>은별색인쇄, 그리고 후공정</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3505b336-5728-435f-8305-578fdaec65a6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9727c528-7eab-4f12-84a9-15e32077aa4d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">은별색인쇄 샘플을 통해서 여러가지 후공정이나 방법을 설명드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-82c2f6a9-1c81-4f46-b8b3-4220b08310f5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222901405843/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-31932b1a-a371-440e-b40d-09f13353e16c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3f000165-7ac2-40b9-bd7d-62f6a05694b7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e0aca2ab-e6af-4b77-a8d2-2a2390e94eb0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-25694b1b-dd51-42a3-8285-145c37b81ae3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-22dcb6d8-fa92-452f-a474-80bdac2d1646\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-99c14ed5-0105-4474-8191-dc539c91e6f2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cea39ed1-58e9-4cc2-895f-b52c72227773\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3822937b-9663-4fff-a6a3-5e3d131e3d6e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-93383030-2299-4d24-9f82-636d07695b82\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>종이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7fcb3ad9-9ba8-4a6a-bd2c-5c2b8e36b3ed\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e2ebfdae-5660-4a66-9e72-915cce4fcb90\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이가 너무 얇을 경우 돌돌 말리는 현상이 발생할 수 있습니다. 이 현상은 한쪽으로 코팅을 하면 더 심해지며 해결하는 방법이 그렇게 많이 있지는 않습니다. 종이 평량의 특성상 수축과 말림 현상은 자연스러우며 습기가 많은 여름에 인쇄를 하고 진행할 경우 흔히 말해 종이 바가지(?) 현상이 심하게 일어나 인쇄를 하기 어려울 수 있습니다. 종이는 습기에 매우 취약하므로 크린룸 시스템이나 cip시스템 도입등으로 인쇄의 품질을 꾸준하게 유지하기 위한 노력을 많이 하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-af9819b2-4e00-49a3-9fc9-4e1a9bed85bc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f4809993-f060-46ef-a2f9-44a384c4fabc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8dd8fecc-6e5d-4648-86ac-db3f12a49bca\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4f68cee5-128e-448d-b8a1-2ac6567e855b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-afc089d2-fd92-4746-b279-9e0103895b7f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5eb3e6c7-79ba-42e2-8102-bf3b4512f6a0\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>먹 베다 인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2d751b15-cddd-4633-8acd-d8071e68d268\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fec3a0b4-7170-4b09-882e-6b7adf0d3a02\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄는 베다(바탕)와 아미(%)라는 용어를 사용하여 인쇄의 농도를 이야기합니다. 베다는 CMYK의 색상이 100%일때를 말합니다. K100% 베다를 우리는 먹  베다(100%)라고 말합니다. 먹 잉크 100%를 인쇄하는것 보다 CMYK100%를 함께 인쇄하면 더 진한색으로 인쇄할 수 있습니다. 다만 뒷묻음 현상으로 우리는 무광먹 별색 잉크로 인쇄하고 무광 라미네이팅으로 뒷묻음을 방지했습니다. 베다와 아미, 그라데이션(보카시)등은 추후 자세히 설명하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a2c262a7-e3e5-4057-a870-78c6fe7eea94\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f98ad0f7-6a01-43d0-958d-16a0189d3c97\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cfc269a1-b428-4fcb-a13e-3a4b919fab7c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3d131e48-0ab1-4b7d-b9ad-ce9b14a0b002\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-cda734b2-8000-4813-a338-d003af783499\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-487d0022-77c3-4382-89db-84b2e64b6e41\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4608aafd-7213-4c68-a4d6-70cf35a265fa\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-067dad99-8b73-4aa4-8d84-7e3b2f7a262e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>작업시 알아야할 사양</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cdf55947-88fb-4b18-a823-61444b400cd4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6a2e2438-ecbc-4fd2-913e-c5007b170151\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄시 반드시 알아야하는 사양은 다음과 같습니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니 사이트 개발시에도 다음을 적용하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-207a2510-8b33-44af-b087-f78140c5c03e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b876ffee-b970-434e-ac7a-8b122104e186\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-547cc763-e834-4637-b671-3af2b8acdf80\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-8e6a6dba-7627-49be-8cdc-14eccc6a4219\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>· 템플릿 번호 : 기본 사양, 페이지, 사이즈, 디자인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f50ed83d-eb29-40a5-84d4-e281c7a26751\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-f5de332c-1751-4710-a4b6-c9c4af289cc4\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-75e50de9-8082-4d94-89f2-3a633d55253c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-d1eb64a2-8338-4077-bfd7-9af534e989d8\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>· 종이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2fd6928a-9329-4372-bb11-25e8dddf14d3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-71ab108e-88ba-4290-8acb-e10cd4b22635\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>· 인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ff7ec1be-8275-43fb-aef8-87d96428905e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-6312b4ce-e66f-419b-9248-9e7229448a9c\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>· 후가공</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ae5376e-592c-4255-a644-425ea9e4d17c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-73786d50-6853-4f72-b46a-00f47accd530\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>· 수량</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b7243d74-7d26-4a79-b72d-5ef0f0223621\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-c4469031-b7c4-435d-9487-9df17d94ebee\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-41cc46a0-b732-4dfc-8bf6-07ee15c321f9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-63742a6e-ed36-46c2-820c-b6c619af068f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-ae5c7752-d7b7-4bb7-b2be-75467a9dba2c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-07693390-4c6b-4ad8-805e-35346cd0c34b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-af108311-292e-4abf-85f4-1dbaed989bac\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니이 찾는 리퍼럴(referral)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-27ea7991-62a4-4a98-b874-f015985f1f90\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-81ed15cc-bcb0-4e6b-9f26-2a56f7e6d064\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-37d6e2aa-88d6-4586-a3a2-b4629643a12b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니이 찾는 리퍼럴은?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-140136b2-e6ff-498a-9827-340f1c7271ca\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ade669de-85bb-4c7f-b091-78448e198c38\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">고급스러운 홍보물을 원하는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e5b86a1e-44d1-45ce-b438-14025e29f781\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>고객관리용 안내장 제작 담당자</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-cdf1b19e-dffb-40c4-aa4a-5e7b0bccd728\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
